  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a prospective observational trial. The purpose of this study is to explore the&#xD;
      feasibility of EIT monitoring pulmonary blood flow and the consistency and difference between&#xD;
      EIT monitoring pulmonary local ventilation blood flow and SPECT and CTPA monitoring methods&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
